list process that has the same tty as current one
ps

list process that has tty
ps a

list process that has tty in forest, add extra PPID column
ps af -O ppid

list all process
ps aux

list process by command name (full match)
ps -C vim

list process by process id, show pid, pgid, ppid, stat, cmd only
ps -123 -o pid,pgid,ppid,stat,cmd
